title: Papyrus Graduation Card (Exciting and Bright Future)
description: Send happy and heartfelt wishes to your favorite grad with this premium card from Papyrus! Inspirational words and festive balloons are featured in the colorful design, which is embellished with shimmering foil and includes a special charm attachment. The inside message sends along the very best wishes to the graduate and looks beautiful in gold lettering. This awesome card is perfect for grads of all levels and comes with a lovely blue-green envelope that complements the art. Extra postage is required and the unique Papyrus gold seal is included.
